      <title>随着美国期货的上升：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心唐纳德·特朗普总统的贸易战风险冒着全球经济增长的危险，亚洲市场周二面临的波动率更高。美国期货在早期交易中上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 22:42:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
