    <item>
      <title>巴菲特的2025年财富在亿万富翁的消灭中脱颖而出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/buffett-s-2025-wealth-gains-stand-out-amid-billionaire-wipeout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在世界上最富有的人群中，沃伦·巴菲特（Warren Buffett）是少数几位在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税引发抛售后，今年个人命运已成长的少数人之一，从而从全球股票中删除了数万亿美元的价值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/buffett-s-2025-wealth-gains-stand-out-amid-billionaire-wipeout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 22:14:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当关税斯托克经济衰退恐惧时，COMEX铜进入熊市市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/comex-copper-enters-bear-market-as-tariffs-stoke-recession-fear</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在纽约交易的铜连续第三天跌落，这与3月下旬最近的高点相比下降了20％，并标志着美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的广泛关税引起了人们对经济衰退的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/comex-copper-enters-bear-market-as-tariffs-stoke-recession-fear</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 21:48:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自特朗普当选以来，美元树篱的成本飙升至最高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/cost-of-dollar-hedges-soars-to-highest-since-trump-s-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贸易商急于购买对美元秋千的保护，将对冲成本推向自去年11月唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）当选以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/cost-of-dollar-hedges-soars-to-highest-since-trump-s-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 16:38:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
